Men were formerly the citizens of Canifis. If players were not wielding a wolfbane dagger when attacking them, they would turn into wolfmen.

In 2007, werewolves were graphically updated. The men were replaced by new named citizens, while the Wolfmen were replaced by werewolves. As a result, they have never been present in Old School RuneScape.

'''Men''' were formerly the citizens of [[Canifis]]. If players were not wielding a [[wolfbane dagger]] when attacking them, they would turn into [[Wolfman|wolfmen]].

In 2007, werewolves were graphically updated. The men were replaced by new named citizens, while the Wolfmen were replaced by [[werewolves]]. As a result, they have never been present in ''Old School RuneScape''.
